	&lt;div class="note-icon">
		
	&lt;/div>
	&lt;div class="admonition-content">&lt;p>Most of the commands for &lt;strong>Hugo Modules&lt;/strong> require a newer version (&amp;gt;= 1.18) of Go installed (see &lt;a href="https://golang.org/dl/" rel="external">https://golang.org/dl/&lt;/a>) and the relevant VCS client (e.g. Git, see &lt;a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads/" rel="external">https://git-scm.com/downloads/&lt;/a> ).
If you have an &amp;ldquo;older&amp;rdquo; site running on Netlify, you may have to set GO_VERSION to 1.19 or newer in your Environment settings.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Theme components</title><link>https://gohugo.io/hugo-modules/theme-components/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/hugo-modules/theme-components/</guid><description>&lt;p>

&lt;aside>
 &lt;div class="admonition-content bl bw2 b--blue" >
