 &lt;/div>
&lt;/aside>

Since Hugo &lt;code>0.42&lt;/code> a project can configure a theme as a composite of as many theme components you need:&lt;/p>

&lt;div class="code relative" id="hugo">
 &lt;div class="code-nav flex flex-nowrap items-stretch">
 &lt;div class="san-serif f6 dib lh-solid pl2 pv2 mr2">
 hugo.
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;button
 data-toggle-tab="yaml"
 class="tab-button active ba san-serif f6 dib lh-solid ph2 pv2">
 yaml
 &lt;/button>
 &amp;nbsp;
 &lt;button
 data-toggle-tab="toml"
 class="tab-button ba san-serif f6 dib lh-solid ph2 pv2">
 toml
 &lt;/button>
 &amp;nbsp;
 &lt;button
 data-toggle-tab="json"
 class="tab-button ba san-serif f6 dib lh-solid ph2 pv2">
 json
 &lt;/button>
 &amp;nbsp;
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="tab-content">
 &lt;div
 data-pane="yaml"
 class="code-copy-content nt3 tab-pane active">
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nt">theme&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">my-shortcodes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">base-theme&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">hyde&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div
 data-pane="toml"
 class="code-copy-content nt3 tab-pane ">
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-toml" data-lang="toml">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nx">theme&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;my-shortcodes&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;base-theme&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;hyde&amp;#39;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;div
 data-pane="json"
 class="code-copy-content nt3 tab-pane ">
 &lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;theme&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;my-shortcodes&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;base-theme&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;hyde&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;/div>

&lt;p>You can even nest this, and have the theme component itself include theme components in its own &lt;code>hugo.toml&lt;/code> (theme inheritance).&lt;sup id="fnref:1">&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref">1&lt;/a>&lt;/sup>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>